divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving 3 miles outside of downtown Freeport,IL when I thought I saw something move fast into the clouds. I stopped and just snapped a photo. I thought through my DSLR screen I could see something but wasnt sure until I got back home some 7 or so hours later. There are 2 photos, the first untouched and the 2nd AUTO Adjusted through Photoshop. It appears as a semi-transparent shuttle-like craft to me. All the spots are from dust on my lens.
Summary: UFO Discovered after viewing photos back home.
